The college administrators are cheating the country and the government.
The prosecutor &amp; apos; s office of the East Kazakhstan region conducted an inspection of the activities of colleges in the region , which revealed numerous violations of the law , as well as the fact of misuse of budget funds .
In particular , the facts of non-compliance with the competitive procedures for placing the state order , false teaching of students , illegal granting of grants , non-compliance of teachers with the qualification requirements , non-provision of students with dormitories , as well as illegal rental of state property were revealed .
Often there is a falsification of data on the number of graduates employed by artificially increasing the number of graduates , and the administration of educational institutions does not provide assistance in employment of graduates .
Despite the fact that the rules of placement of the state educational order were violated , in particular , students from other regions were not provided with dormitories , the regional education department annually awarded grants to the College of Business and Service in Semey , the Polytechnic College in Ayagoz and two colleges in Ust-Kamenogorsk .
The administration of the college included in the price of accommodation of students in the dormitory the costs for utilities included in the total amount of the contract for the state order , rented rooms in the dormitories to third parties .
Twelve students were falsely enrolled at my neighborhood college.
Teachers and masters of industrial training assessed these students in theoretical and practical training journals during the training sessions, sent them to intermediate certification, transferred from course to course.
In addition , scholarships were paid to these students , the total amount of damage to the state amounted to 8 million tenge .
A pre-trial investigation is being conducted on this fact .
Facts of illegal use of property for personal purposes were also detected on the territory of the college .
For example, on the territory of the East Kazakhstan Regional Art School named after the brothers Abdullins , people ' s artists , there is a long-term paid parking lot .
After the prosecutor's recommendation, the parking lot will be closed and a sports ground will be built in its place.
According to the results of the inspection , prosecutors have established a damage of more than 43 million tenge .
To date , 36 million tenge has been recovered under supervision acts .
60 persons were brought to disciplinary responsibility , 4 persons were brought to administrative responsibility .
